io.netty.util.collection

Interface LongObjectMap<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type stored in the map.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Map<Long,V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LongObjectHashMap

    public interface LongObjectMap<V>
extends Map<Long,V>
    Interface for a primitive map that uses longs as keys.

      • entries

        Iterable<LongObjectMap.PrimitiveEntry<V>> entries()
        Gets an iterable to traverse over the primitive entries contained in this map. As an optimization, the LongObjectMap.PrimitiveEntrys returned by the Iterator may change as the Iterator progresses. The caller should not rely on LongObjectMap.PrimitiveEntry key/value stability.
